      <strong>Natural Listening</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Hear real speech speed, pitch accent, and connected sounds</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #f0fdf4; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">🎭</div>
      <strong>Register Awareness</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Learn formal, casual, and keigo speech in context</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #fefce8; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">🇯🇵</div>
      <strong>Cultural Learning</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Understand social norms, etiquette, and daily life</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #fdf2f8; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
