  <p>Start with a beginner drama from the list above and commit to the active watching method this week. Use our <a href="/japanese/tools/jlpt-vocabulary/">JLPT Vocabulary tool</a> to check and study the words you encounter, and explore our <a href="/japanese/blog/japanese-resources-2026/">Best Japanese Resources guide</a> for more tools to support your learning journey.</p>

